{"tid":545692,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友呀，其實我好愛你","createTime":"2018-01-30T18:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T18:36:57.000Z","uid":860,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7388e41c920f9e2f5bdfc4b8273d181dd8d3f138","tid":545692,"uid":860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T18:17:53.000Z","msg":"雖然你成日都返咁長工，但你寧願自己搵自己洗唔想下下我用錢<br />\n雖然你乜撚都唔識煮，但煮個公仔麵比我都已經夠<br />\n雖然有時我放假你返工，但你都調早更等收工同我行街食飯到夜晚<br />\n雖然你有啲煩，但係每句都係為我好<br />\n雖然你有好多朋友，但都願意將大部分時間用黎陪我<br />\n雖然有時你好蠢，但我笑完你又唔會嬲<br />\n我又唔靚仔又無才華又無錢又唔上進，但你都肯同我一齊<br />\n我愛你呀女朋友<br />\n叫完春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062bf38c9389ea39b2f8a5de4a46e208eb28934b","tid":545692,"uid":98915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T18:31:45.000Z","msg":"祝樓主早日帶帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f624d61cf6ee5091334ab29aee7f9bf1f507be0c","tid":545692,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T18:32:57.000Z","msg":"好快分手"},{"pid":"9aefb76e736637a3f97a2facf6a6cebf88a7d58f","tid":545692,"uid":115930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T18:36:57.000Z","msg":"樓主我認得你，你點會無錢啊，有錢可以去到twice簽售，我不知幾羨慕你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}